OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with a few showery
OL,7,Fbands of rain spreading northeast.
OL,8,FSome drier and clearer spells will
OL,9,Fthen develop during the rest of the
OL,10,Fnight. Freshening southerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FPartly cloudy with showery
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, some may be on the
OL,14,Fheavy side in the west. Drier,
OL,15,Fbrighter around the Moray Firth.
OL,16,FRather breezy, occasionally strong on
OL,17,Fwest coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
